---
import CMG5 from "../../assets/images/ColdMix/GallerySlider/CMG5.webp";
import CMVideo from "../../assets/images/ColdMix/CMVideo.mp4";  
---
<div class="w-full flex flex-col justify-center">
    <div class="w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 flex flex-col justify-center items-center font-bold">
        <div class="text-end lg:w-1/2 md:w-1/2 mt-24 self-end">
            <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl">COLD MIX ASPHALT PLANTS</h1><br>
            <div class="h-0.5 bg-blueMain w-full"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-full grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 py-10 gap-6">
            <div class="mt-6">
                <p class="text-blueMain text-base md:text-lg">
                    Triaso® cold mix plants are specifically engineered to produce aggregate mixtures without applying heat.
                    Using a robust pugmill mixer, these plants blend unheated aggregates with asphalt emulsion or other
                    liquid binders to deliver a uniform, durable mix suitable for a variety of applications.
                    <br><br>
                    Equipped with precision dosing hoppers, they ensure accurate control of material proportions, providing
                    consistent performance across every batch. Their capability to handle different aggregate types makes
                    them well-suited for patching, road maintenance, and small-scale paving applications.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full flex justify-center">
                <img src={CMG5.src} alt="" class="w-full h-auto object-contain">
            </div>
        </div>
        
    
    </div>
    <div class="w-full flex justify-center">
        <div class="max-w-7xl bg-grisT rounded-xl p-8 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 items-center justify-center gap-10">
            <div class="w-full text-white flex flex-col gap-3 justify-center">
                <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold">Cold Mixing = Eco-Friendly Mix</h1>
                <div class="w-full h-0.5 bg-white"></div>
                <p class="text-base md:text-lg">
                    Designed for efficiency and flexibility, quick setup, and minimal maintenance, cold mix plants provide
                    a reliable solution for contractors, municipalities, and remote projects — delivering consistent aggregate
                    mix production whenever required, with the ease of not needing to heat the aggregates.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full flex justify-center rounded-2xl overflow-hidden self-center">
                <video class="lg:w-3/4 md:w-3/4 rounded-2xl" src={CMVideo} autoplay controls></video>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>